00:20:59,458 --> 00:21:01,708
I don't know how to thank you
for all you've done for me.

505
00:21:01,791 --> 00:21:02,708
[MUTSUMI]
There's no need.

506
00:21:02,791 --> 00:21:04,708
Will you apologize
to your brother?

507
00:21:04,791 --> 00:21:06,875
I acted so rudely to him.

508
00:21:06,958 --> 00:21:08,500
I don't think
you were rude at all.

509
00:21:08,583 --> 00:21:09,875
He had it coming!

510
00:21:11,416 --> 00:21:13,000
[MUTSUMI]
Oh, I got this for you.

511
00:21:13,083 --> 00:21:14,250
It's for the test.

512
00:21:16,083 --> 00:21:18,000
[MUTSUMI] If you're ever torn
between different options,

513
00:21:18,083 --> 00:21:19,541
this will help.

514
00:21:19,625 --> 00:21:21,791
You can tilt luck in your favor.

515
00:21:21,875 --> 00:21:23,000
[chuckles]

516
00:21:24,291 --> 00:21:25,958
What a wonderful present!

517
00:21:27,541 --> 00:21:28,750
[MUTSUMI]
Oh... you three.

518
00:21:29,958 --> 00:21:31,375
Here's one for each of you.

519
00:21:31,458 --> 00:21:33,625
Good luck on all of your tests.

520
00:21:33,708 --> 00:21:35,625
Wow. Thanks a lot.

521
00:21:35,708 --> 00:21:37,041
[IGARASHI] That was the
most fun I've ever had

522
00:21:37,125 --> 00:21:39,666
in a girl's bedroom,
and all we did was study!

523
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:40,666
Unbelievable.

524
00:21:40,750 --> 00:21:42,166
[NANASHIMA]
Tonight was awesome.

525
00:21:48,833 --> 00:21:50,750
This is his way of apologizing?

526
00:21:50,833 --> 00:21:51,875
Forgiven.

527
00:21:53,583 --> 00:21:55,666
I passed!
No summer classes for me!

528
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:57,625
This girl is ready for vacation!

529
00:21:57,708 --> 00:21:59,666
[GROUP]
Congratulations!

530
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:01,208
We should go hang
out at the pool!

531
00:22:01,291 --> 00:22:02,916
That sounds like a good idea!

532
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,125
Just the two of us!

533
00:22:04,208 --> 00:22:06,416
There are historical
sites we could visit.

534
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:07,958
[SERINUMA]
Uh...

535
00:22:08,041 --> 00:22:09,458
[SERINUMA]
And so I chose... 

536
00:22:09,541 --> 00:22:11,250
[SERINUMA, NAKANO screaming]

537
00:22:11,333 --> 00:22:14,208
You're the greatest
boy band ever!

538
00:22:14,291 --> 00:22:16,791
[SERINUMA] To attend every
single one of the otaku events

539
00:22:16,875 --> 00:22:18,000
with A!

540
00:23:50,500 --> 00:23:51,375
[SHINOMIYA]
When I was a kid,

541
00:23:51,458 --> 00:23:52,666
I stayed down in
the dumps a lot.

542
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:54,041
[MUTSUMI]
Why?

543
00:23:54,125 --> 00:23:54,833
[SHINOMIYA] People teased me
for being too delicate!

544
00:23:54,916 --> 00:23:56,208
It was frustrating.

545
00:23:56,291 --> 00:23:57,166
[NANASHIMA] Yeah, well I've
always pretty popular

546
00:23:57,250 --> 00:23:58,166
because of soccer.

547
00:23:58,250 --> 00:23:59,750
Igarashi has me beat though.

548
00:23:59,833 --> 00:24:01,708
[IGARASHI] That's because I'm
still playing in high school!

549
00:24:01,791 --> 00:24:02,791
Why did you ever quit?

550
00:24:02,875 --> 00:24:04,333
[NANASHIMA]
It's exhausting!

551
00:24:04,416 --> 00:24:06,541
How am supposed to do that plus
everything else I wanna do?

552
00:24:06,625 --> 00:24:07,666
[MUTSUMI]
That reminds me--

553
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:09,500
The cultural festival
is coming up.

554
00:24:09,583 --> 00:24:11,208
There are so many
fun things there!

555
00:24:11,291 --> 00:24:13,000
[SHINOMIYA] Unless you're
stuck having to wear a dress.

556
00:24:13,083 --> 00:24:15,041
[NANASHIMA] Aww, but you're
such a pretty princess!

557
00:24:15,125 --> 00:24:16,333
[SHINOMIYA]
Do you ever stop talking?

558
00:24:16,416 --> 00:24:17,666
[IGARASHI]
Dress or no dress,

559
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:19,375
I'm pumped to see what's
going on at the festival!

